snippet.title: SONIC STORM TIME TRIAL TESTFIRE TRAILER + DUAL STORY DEMO RERELEASE
snippet.description:
The Time Trial Testfire is coming out! You'll finally be able to play Sonic Storm for the first time! Since it's Christmas, I've also decided to package a special surprise with it too!

The Time Trial Testfire: https://drive.google.com/file/d/1bmQjvSRqFUROxrlk5epfoh7qVeBAXyTV/view?usp=sharing
The Old Dual Story Demo: https://drive.google.com/file/d/1VyrSAOAvFPYGFVRd7fxbmGkyFFm7Jkyn/view?usp=sharing
